snippet.title: The Hungry Town - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
The Hungry Town - visual novel quest from a young indie team Kick Punch Games.

One ordinary evening you receive a message on your phone that sets off a series of strange and confusing events. In the end you have to choose the right side or stay true to yourself.

Add to your Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2481160

Twitter/X - twitter.com/oshpunch
Discord - https://discord.gg/DCu2x7xSsG
